title: Basil Pesto & Roast Pumpkin Couscous with Lemon-Chilli Pangrattato & Crumbly Cheese
description: Risoni – the clever pasta that looks like rice – is the ideal ingredient in this warm bowl. With butternut pumpkin and courgette, this dinner filled with goodness gets the welcome addition of crumbly cheese and basil pesto to really raise the flavour stakes.

